room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: My husband and I celebrated our anniversary trying to BREAK OUT! Sadly, Esmerelda stole our souls. We had a BLAST and our marriage is still tact lol. We will def be back. The staff was friendly and made it great

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: We had so much fun!! What a great team building exercise!! Will definitely be back!!

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: Soooo fun! There's something for everyone in every room! You don't have to be a wizard with puzzles or math, but you do need to search and think quickly!

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: This is a must do! Everyone should have it on there bucketlist!

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: This was my first time doing an escape the room challenge and I loved it! It really makes you think and work together as a team. The room was well decorated and the host was very engaging. I can't wait to go back and do another!

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: So much fun even though we failed! If we'd only had 5 more minutes! Highly recommended for families who are looking for something different to do!

room_title: Escape room "Double Agent Dilemma" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
review: We loved this and can't wait to go back! All of our group contributed and got out with just under 3 minutes to spare. Hope to go back and do another one soon
